Subject: BIOS hacking with the Raspberry Pi
Description: Using the Raspberry Pi as an inexpensive eeprom programmer to hack a Macbook's BIOS.  Speakers include:Stephen Gualdoni - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector

Subject: Why Can't Ashley Sing
Description: This talk will demonstrate the technologies used in a modern recording studio to make the difference between the sound musicians make live and what you hear in recordings.  Speakers include:Stephen Gualdoni - Track: Tech, Music  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector
